{"tid":1965911,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲野過去左，就唔好勉強","createTime":"2020-04-09T19:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T00:51:23.000Z","uid":221104,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"59d58fb269055ef594449685513344f9183314e6","tid":1965911,"uid":221104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T19:24:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uzrtS1je_rw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuzrtS1je_rw&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=88391526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uzrtS1je_rw</a><br />\n<br />\n有啲野過去左，就唔好勉強<br />\n辛苦既只係你自己；<br />\n如果你比人帽／比人飛／飛人都好，<br />\n過去左，錯過左，真係唔好挽回／挽番；<br />\n<br />\n愛你又點會傷害你？<br />\n傷害得你，其實又點會係真正愛你？<br />\n<br />\n你唔信唔緊要，<br />\n路，始終都要你自己行；<br />\n<br />\n到有一日如果 您 同我地一樣身受重傷個時，<br />\n你就可能會明白咩叫<br />\n<br />\n「早知道是這樣 像夢一場 <br />\n我才不會把愛都放在同一個地方<br />\n我能原諒 你的荒唐 <br />\n荒唐的是我沒有辦法遺忘」<br />\n<br />\n雖然就黎　「世界末日」<br />\n但你自己<br />\n<br />\n都愛自己多啲啦 巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75129bba026d08d4d46c3324c68bd610e2cac1f7","tid":1965911,"uid":308811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T20:21:29.000Z","msg":"珍"},{"pid":"66916bd0127c202ed1bf67b583a42742c52ce7e2","tid":1965911,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T21:10:21.000Z","msg":"駁5到"},{"pid":"a48779ed33fe4cc3518e53915df44b370870a369","tid":1965911,"uid":168750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T21:11:36.000Z","msg":"Rea